# 🚗 Vehicle Information System

A console‑based Java application that manages different vehicle types (cars, motorcycles, trucks) for a car rental agency. Demonstrates **interfaces**, **encapsulation**, **input validation**, and **enums**.

## ✨ Features

- **Car** – store make, model, year, number of doors, fuel type (Petrol/Diesel/Electric)
- **Motorcycle** – store wheels (2 or 3) and type (Sport/Cruiser/Off‑road)
- **Truck** – store cargo capacity (tons) and transmission (Manual/Automatic)
- **Input validation** – year between 1886 and next year, doors 2‑6, wheels 2‑3, capacity 0‑100 tons
- **Enums** for fuel type, motorcycle type, transmission – no invalid strings
- **User‑friendly prompts** – re‑prompts on invalid input instead of crashing

## 🛠️ Requirements

- Java JDK 11 or higher

